<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Support Computerbank through donations, volunteering, or partnerships to help bridge the digital divide.">
    <title>Support Us - <%= company.name %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./public/css/main.css">
    <%- include('partials/favicon-stylesheet') %>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS for Carousel -->
    <!--    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">-->
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/jumbotron') %>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<!-- Main Content -->
<div class="container my-5">
    <section>
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Our Ebay Store</h2>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                <p>
                    <span class="fw-bold"><%= company.name %></span> sells equipment on Ebay that is not useful for low income or community groups. These items may be bulky, faulty, vintage, enterprise equipment, one of a kind or end of life equipment. Laptops listed have issues or have marks and scratches. Excess stock is also sold.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We are a not-for-profit organisation. All funds raised by sales go back towards our operating costs.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We are self-funded and receive no financial support from business or government. By selling these items, we stop them from going into landfill.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                <img src="/images/recycling-4-300x225.jpg" alt="Recycling" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<!-- Bootstrap JS -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>